<translate><!--T:304--> The rendering of a given group can be customized across the wiki by creating {{<tvar name=1>tmpl|0={{blue|MediaWiki:Cite_link_label_group-&lt;$1>}}</tvar>|name}} and listing the used signs in the order they appear, separated by spaces or newlines.</translate>
